    <div class="recipe-description">
     
     <img src="benef4.jpg" alt="imag" class="imag">
     
     <p> A Bad Habit is a negative behaviour pattern. Common Examples include: Eating Junk Food 24/7, Dessert, Being Lazy, Etc.
