     <p>Obesity: An Estimated 160 million Americans are either obese or overweight. Nearly three quarters of American men and more than 60% of women are obese or overweight. These are also major challenges for America's children-nearly 30% of boys and girls under age 20 are either obese or overweight.
            Cure: Eat Healthy & Workout Continuesly
     </p>
